Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:44.30,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}向着前方大声说出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:50.70,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}这份心情没有错误
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:58.90,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}鼓起勇气 一路前行
